 ${python3:Depends},
 python3-systemd
Description: small admin CLI for reading systemd journal entries
 Journal Admin is a small command-line tool that reads recent systemd journal
 entries through the APT-managed python3-systemd binding. It is packaged for
 the system Python interpreter because its runtime dependency comes from the
 operating system package manager rather than from PyPI.
